### Depth {#a275a5f7ce41d40c967288d74c6487b8b}

<MemberDefinition
  template={<>template &lt;typename ContextT&gt;</>}
  prototype={<>unsigned llvm::GenericCycle&lt; ContextT &gt;::Depth = 0</>}>
Depth of the cycle in the tree.

The root &quot;cycle&quot; is at depth 0.


:::info
Depths are not necessarily contiguous. However, child loops always have strictly greater depth than their parents, and sibling loops always have the same depth.
:::

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/genericcycleinfo-h/#l00075">75</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/genericcycleinfo-h">GenericCycleInfo.h</a>.
